name: vbs23-avs1
hint: Find indoor shots of three or more people sitting around the same table with food on it.

name: vbs23-avs2
hint: Find shots of only one person either riding a horse or riding a horse-drawn cart, without other people visible.

name: vbs23-avs3
hint: Find shots of an adult person running in an (sub-)urban street. Cars may be visible, but no other persons walking or running.

name: vbs23-avs4
hint: Find shots of one or more adult persons holding, releasing, throwing or playing with a balloon of any shape. Balls of any kind are not balloons, air balloons are not included.

name: vbs23-avs5
hint: Find shots showing at least one person singing and at least one drummer (not necessarily playing the drums at that moment).

name: vbs23-avs6
hint: Find shots taken by a paraglider or parachuter, where their shadow (the glider and/or the person) is visible on the ground or water.

name: vbs23-avs7
hint: Find shots showing a bar chart (vertical or horizontal bars).
